STARBURSTS
Episode IV, A FRESH DREAM 
It is a time of domestic squabbles.

Rebel balloons, launching from a concealed clubhouse, have achieved their inaugural triumph over the naughty Galactic Consortium.
During the skirmish, Rebel gossips managed to snag confidential blueprints to the Consortium's peak gadget, the LIFE STAR,

a shielded space hangout with sufficient force to obliterate an entire island.

Chased by the Consortium's crafty consultants, Princess Lulu zooms home aboard her spaceship, holder of the snagged blueprints that can aid her folks and rejuvenate liberty to the universe...
